# Internship Task 3 — Linear Regression
**Author:** Shreshtha Bhusanur  
**Dataset:** Housing Price Prediction (Kaggle)

## Objective
Implement simple & multiple linear regression models, evaluate using MAE, MSE and R², and interpret coefficients.

## Files
- `task3_linear_regression.ipynb` — notebook with code and explanations  
- `housing.csv` — dataset (Kaggle)  
- `plots/` — PNGs of regression line, residuals, etc.  
- `models/` — saved models (optional)

## How to run
1. Clone repo and navigate to task3:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/shreshthabhusanur/internship-task1-shreshtha.git
   cd internship-task1-shreshtha/task3
   jupyter lab task3_linear_regression.ipynb

